data.description: Welcome to the highly sought-after community of Rancho Silverado located minutes from dining, shopping, and direct access to the 303 freeway. With 2800 sq. ft. of living space, 4 beds + Loft, 2.5 baths, this home has ample space to spread out. Conveniently located on a corner lot across from a sprawling green space. Modern gray/cool color scheme throughout, white trim, gray tile floors, and carpets, with dark bronze light fixtures/fans. The main level features gray tile flooring throughout, with a living/front room, family room, dining area, powder room, and updated kitchen. The kitchen features granite counters, a tile backsplash, white cabinets, stainless steel sink, and a walk-in pantry. Spacious master suite and master bath, with dual sinks, separate soaking tub and shower... and a walk-in closet. 3 additional bedrooms and loft space with a handy upper-level laundry room. The backyard is perfectly divided, with a fenced pool area on one side, an extended brick paver patio, and a fire pit seating area with open green space on the other side. Side yard for additional storage and RV gate. This is one of those homes that has it all, so don't miss your opportunity to make it yours.
